## **RESPONSIVE BEHAVIOR SPECIFICATIONS**

### **Mobile-First Adaptations**

#### **Mobile (320-767px)**
- Hamburger menu (full screen)
- Vertical project cards
- Simplified statistics
- Touch-optimized CTAs
- Vertical scrolling only

#### **Tablet (768-1023px)**
- Condensed navigation
- 2-column grids
- Reduced parallax
- Maintained animations

#### **Desktop (1024px+)**
- Full experience
- Horizontal scrolling sections
- All animations active
- Mega-menus enabled

---

## **PERFORMANCE OPTIMIZATION REQUIREMENTS**

### **Loading Strategy**
```
Priority 1 (Above Fold):
- Navigation
- Hero text
- Hero image (optimized)
- Scroll indicator

Priority 2 (Near Fold):
- Statistics
- Introduction text
- First project image

Priority 3 (Below Fold):
- Additional projects
- Videos
- Gallery images
- Map integration
```

