## **QUALITY ASSURANCE BENCHMARKS**

### **Comparison Standards**

**Must Equal or Exceed:**
| Metric | Oxford Properties | Silverstein | Jun's Target |
|--------|------------------|-------------|--------------|
| Load Time | 2.8s | 3.2s | < 2.5s |
| Mobile Score | 85 | 82 | > 90 |
| Accessibility | 88 | 85 | > 95 |
| SEO Score | 92 | 90 | > 95 |

