## **DEVELOPMENT PHASES ADJUSTMENT**

### **Phase 1: Foundation (Week 1-2)**
- Implement Oxford-style navigation
- Create hero video section
- Build statistics dashboard
- Set up project architecture

### **Phase 2: Core Pages (Week 3-4)**
- Homepage with all sections
- Projects gallery with filters
- Individual project templates
- About with timeline

### **Phase 3: Enhancements (Week 5-6)**
- Interactive elements
- Animation implementation
- Performance optimization
- Testing and launch

---

## **AGENT COLLABORATION NOTES**

### **Critical Success Factors**

**Frontend Agent:**
- Study Oxford's scroll behavior closely
- Implement smooth transitions between sections
- Ensure video backgrounds work on all devices
- Create reusable component library

**Backend Agent:**
- Optimize image delivery (WebP, AVIF)
- Implement intelligent lazy loading
- Create efficient project filtering
- Set up CMS for easy updates

**QA Agent:**
- Compare directly against Oxford/Silverstein
- Test on same devices/browsers
- Measure actual load times
- Verify all animations perform smoothly

